:StateOff  # Default anim bc it's the first defined
animation Goto_Off
loop      0
trans     goto_on    StateOn
event     0.0        EventPlaySFXBonk
event     0.999      EventEnableCanBeAttacked

:StateOn
animation Goto_On
loop      0
trans     goto_off   StateOff
event     0.0        EventPlaySFXBonk
event     0.999      EventEnableCanBeAttacked
